### =========================
### USER PRODUCTS
### =========================

### Get all products
GET {{BASE_URL}}/user/products

###

### Get single product
GET {{BASE_URL}}/user/products/{{PRODUCT_ID}}

### =========================
### CART
### =========================

### Add to cart
POST {{BASE_URL}}/user/cart/add/{{PRODUCT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### Get full cart
GET {{BASE_URL}}/user/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

